name: Barrister Gusky
description: I am a romantic, sensitive woman with a sense of humor and kind,loving,devoted heart and soul.I am able to love and surround the loved ones with my love and support.I like to make my man happy and to be happy with him and people around me, am not afraid of giving and always appreciate what people give to me.I can keep and value the harmony of the relationship and friendship with anybody. I am a good friend to my friends and a good person to talk to.You will never get bored with me because I am fun to be with.I do not drink and do not smoke but i tolerate people who do.
